{"tid":1060662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"焗等Gathering完場　失明者炮轟︰殘廁淪私人樂園","createTime":"2019-03-14T01:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:41:14.000Z","uid":225464,"like":222,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"3754dc40c1f8a24f55f811cbaebe883cc0298843","tid":1060662,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:12:21.000Z","msg":"焗等「聚會」完場 失明者炮轟︰殘廁淪私人樂園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2T0donr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2T0donr&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=c5440ca7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2T0donr</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190314/photo/bkn-20190314081500846-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190314081840\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190314%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190314081500846-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190314081840&h=33b14f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有失明人士感嘆，濫用殘廁的問題嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n濫用殘廁問題嚴重，有失明人士在網上發文控訴，不少人把俗稱殘廁的暢通易達洗手間當作私人的「開心樂園」，令真正有需要的用家深受困擾。<br />\n<br />\n失明人士「麵包」在Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」發貼，指有一班自私的人因貪方便在殘廁內鬼混，怒斥︰「我哋呢班有需要用嘅朋友，要喺門外等你哋快樂玩到夠啦，我哋先有得去廁所，呢個係乜嘢道理」。<br />\n<br />\n「麵包」又批評，不時有人在殘廁吞雲吐霧、雙腳踩上廁所板、又將地下弄得濕漉漉，但很多殘疾人士可能因疾病而需要呼吸機，呼吸系統比一般人弱，行動不便亦難以清潔廁板。這些缺德的行為或增加他們受傷的機會，「呢種無奈、辛苦，有幾多個人會明白體會得到」。<br />\n<br />\n現時部分暢通易達洗手間為避免濫用，均索性上鎖，「麵包」感嘆是「沒辦法中的辦法」，縱感不便，亦寧願預先打電話借用，不願殘廁淪為「部分人嘅開心樂園」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對問題深表關注：「殘廁應該留畀有需要嘅人」、「就算去正常廁所，如果又尿又廁紙，我都嗌救命，可以想像到行動不便嘅人真係好慘」、「啲人要好好檢討吓自私自利、缺乏公德嘅心態」。"},{"pid":"957a72f392bf934dff82a5440ec3198c6cf0751f","tid":1060662,"uid":211461,"like":658,"dislike":2,"score":656,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"可以訪問下公廁界人妻KOL咖啡問佢有咩睇法"},{"pid":"df3352a9937b7ed63552479bb962eeca14705878","tid":1060662,"uid":29080,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"957a72f392bf934dff82a5440ec3198c6cf0751f","tid":1060662,"uid":211461,"like":658,"dislike":2,"score":656,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"可以訪問下公廁界人妻KOL咖啡問佢有咩睇法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fcc7c6e74415726baabf4a2b817da5f586f1d2","tid":1060662,"uid":197337,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"df3352a9937b7ed63552479bb962eeca14705878","tid":1060662,"uid":29080,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"957a72f392bf934dff82a5440ec3198c6cf0751f","tid":1060662,"uid":211461,"like":658,"dislike":2,"score":656,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"可以訪問下公廁界人妻KOL咖啡問佢有咩睇法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"土地問題"},{"pid":"73f6a0c947502dac64bc4f7ad66416fe0a581270","tid":1060662,"uid":4052,"like":181,"dislike":11,"score":170,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"點解失明人會知道人地雙腳踩上廁板?"},{"pid":"bcf0699cfafbed9d477f7d096378fc9f4a5d15b0","tid":1060662,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"就算係普通廁格都長期比廢老霸撚住"},{"pid":"2fa455a94395abda85819c7143cb09a29d8142a8","tid":1060662,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"bcf0699cfafbed9d477f7d096378fc9f4a5d15b0","tid":1060662,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"就算係普通廁格都長期比廢老霸撚住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"要塗鴉鬧廢青<br />\n體諒下"},{"pid":"e004cf185300cdee17b8404f9674147c84fd9bac","tid":1060662,"uid":94501,"like":189,"dislike":2,"score":187,"quote":{"pid":"73f6a0c947502dac64bc4f7ad66416fe0a581270","tid":1060662,"uid":4052,"like":181,"dislike":11,"score":170,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"點解失明人會知道人地雙腳踩上廁板?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"導盲犬話佢知"},{"pid":"ba2b2249a411d6e076c4a042ae8dff1d77782ff6","tid":1060662,"uid